Fog_exceptional_value

xemu version
xemu-0.8.133-26fcbe54f17e496bdf530dad9f237e74e2f943fc
Platform
Ubuntu 24.04.3 LTS - Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-6700K CPU @ 4.00GHz
Renderer
Vulkan
GL info
AMD - AMD Radeon Graphics (radeonsi, gfx1201, LLVM 20.1.2, DRM 3.64, 6.8.0-90-generic) - 4.6 (Core Profile) Mesa 25.0.7-0ubuntu0.24.04.2
GLSL version
4.60
Description
Tests the effects of exceptional values (e.g., inf, nan) on the vertex fog coordinate. Fog is set to bright red.
Each test renders a series of blueish quads with their fog coordinate set to interesting test values to observe the resulting behavior.
Suite class def
src/tests/fog_exceptional_value_tests.h
